Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏成这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆弄起来也更加方便吧
